title: Super Bowl Strategy with Brady Quinn (Football 1/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to talk about the Browns supreme dysfunction (4:00), changing overtime rules (8:00), the Chiefs defensive changes (15:00) and then talk about the Patriots incredible run (35:00) and what they expect to see out in the Super Bowl (42:00).
